abstract: Utah football players Marcel Brooks-Brown and Lo Falemaka are expected to recover after being shot at private party.
lead_paragraph: Lo Falemaka, a sophomore, and Marcel Brooks-Brown, a freshman, were expected to recover, Coach Kyle Whittingham said.

headline.main: Two Utah Football Players Are Shot
